    "description": {
      "value": "<h3>Brutal 1</h3>\n<p>When you score a critical hit with a weapon with the brutal property, you roll a number of additional weapon damage dice equal to the brutal number.</p>\n<h3>Dexterity 19</h3>\n<p>A weapon with this property requires more skill to control. While wielding it, you have disadvantage on attack rolls unless you meet the Dexterity requirement. </p>\n<h3>Heavy</h3>\n<p>When you hit with an attack roll using Strength with a weapon with this property, you deal additional damage equal to half your Strength modifier (minimum of +1).</p>\n<h3>Keen 1</h3>\n<p>When you make a weapon attack with a weapon with the keen property, the critical hit range increases by an amount equal to the keen number.</p>\n<h3>Luminous</h3>\n<p>A weapon with this property sheds dim light in a 5-foot radius while activated. Additionally, Dexterity (Stealth) checks made while the weapon is activated have disadvantage.</p>\n<h3>Reach</h3>\n<p>A weapon with this property adds 5 feet to your reach with it.</p>\n<h3>Two-handed</h3>\n<p>A weapon with this property requires two hands to use.</p>",
